You can soak in a public or a private pool. Everything smells herbal and steamy and itâs SO GOOD for getting your head back on straight.

g.title: j1291611895
g.text: From what Iâve seen, some of them are basically spawning pools now. It breaks my heart, to tell you the truth. I remember finding thousand-year-old marble and mosaic floors carpeted over with creeping flesh.
